"use client" import { useState } from "react" import { Link, useNavigate } from "react-router-dom" import { useAuth } from "../context/AuthContext" const Navbar = () => { const [isMenuOpen, setIsMenuOpen] = useState(false) const { user, logout, isAuthenticated } = useAuth() const navigate = useNavigate() const handleLogout = () => { logout() navigate("/") } return (
{/* Logo */} RealEstate {/* Desktop Navigation */}
Home Buy Sell Rent Properties Calculator
{/* Auth Section */}
{isAuthenticated ? (
Welcome, {user?.name}
) : (
Login Sign Up
)}
) } export default Navbar
